  "instructions": [
    "Preheat your oven to 320°F (160°C).",
    "Mix the granulated sugar, glucose granules, toasted almonds, cinnamon, and salt in a large bowl.",
    "Fold in the coconut flakes and pistachios into the mixture until well combined.",
    "Spread the mixture evenly on a baking sheet lined with parchment paper.",
    "Bake for 25 minutes or until golden brown. Stir halfway through baking to prevent burning.",
    "Let it cool completely before storing in an airtight container."
